text: Seven Sundays is a 2017 Filipino comedy-drama movie directed by Cathy Garcia- Molina and starring Aga Muhlach, Dingdong Dantes, Cristine Reyes, Enrique Gil, Ronaldo Valdez. It was distributed by Star Cinema. ==Other websites== * Category:2017 comedy-drama movies Category:Filipino movies Category:Movies directed by Cathy Garcia-Molina
